B.W4=new A.bK(B.eV,["journaling","Chronal - Journaling App","A highly advanced, technically complex digital journaling platform featuring rich-text HTML rendering, responsive formatting, and a custom WYSIWYG editor. Chronal supports secure local draft versioning and offline-first database synchronization using Hive and SQLite queues. Users can seamlessly embed media, upload and resize images, apply custom paragraph styling block layouts, and auto-save drafts locally, ensuring data integrity even during offline sessions.",!0,B.S6,B.Tx],t.yf)
